QuestData.Title: Reinforcements Incoming...
QuestData.Description: <Hellscream shakes his head.>$B$BYou may not have noticed that we're trying to win a war here, $r. I need all available soldiers at the primary points of conflict. This means that we don't have any real soldiers to spare for these minor incursions.$B$B<Hellscream pauses to think.>$B$BIf Barthus wants reinforcements at the farm...$B$B<Hellscream claps his hands together.>$B$B...he shall have them! Report to Barthus's assassins at the farms, west of here. Let them know that reinforcements have arrived.
QuestData.LogDescription: Seek out Shadowstalker Ickoris at the Warsong Farms Outpost west of Warsong Hold.
QuestData.RewardText: This is it? Hellscream sent a single $r $g boy:girl;?$B$BIf I still had a jaw it would be on the floor right now.
